{"prompt": "Generate a website for a cybersecurity firm. The website should be vibrant and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SecureGuard Cyber Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #e52b50; /* Vibrant Red */\n            --secondary-color: #f08080; /* Light Coral - softer than primary */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --background-color: #1a1a1a;\n            --button-hover-color: #f05f7a;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: var(--primary-color);\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #ccc 3px solid;\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n        }\n\n        header a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            text-transform: uppercase;\n            font-size: 16px;\n        }\n\n        header ul {\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n            list-style: none;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        header li {\n            float: left;\n            display: inline;\n            padding: 0 20px 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header #branding {\n            float: left;\n        }\n\n        header #branding h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 24px;\n        }\n\n        header nav {\n            float: right;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            min-height: 400px;\n            background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517245386807-78429285265f?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            position: relative;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n\n        #hero::before {\n            content: \"\";\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 0;\n            left: 0;\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            background: rgba(229, 43, 80, 0.7); /* Semi-transparent primary color overlay */\n        }\n\n        #hero h1 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 55px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 20px;\n            color: #eee;\n        }\n\n        #services, #about, #contact {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        #services h2, #about h2, #contact h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 36px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item, .about-content {\n            width: 30%;\n            float: left;\n            padding: 20px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            background: #222;\n            margin: 10px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover, .about-content:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            border-top: 3px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item h3, .about-content h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact form {\n            margin-top: 20px;\n        }\n\n        #contact input[type=\"text\"],\n        #contact input[type=\"email\"],\n        #contact textarea {\n            width: 80%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            background: #333;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        #contact button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #contact button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--button-hover-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background: #222;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            border-top: 3px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        @media(max-width: 768px) {\n            header #branding,\n            header nav,\n            header nav ul,\n            header li {\n                float: none;\n                text-align: center;\n                width: 100%;\n            }\n\n            header nav ul li {\n                display: block;\n                padding: 10px 0;\n            }\n\n            #hero h1 {\n                font-size: 40px;\n            }\n\n            .service-item, .about-content {\n                width: 80%;\n                float: none;\n                margin: 20px auto;\n            }\n\n            #contact input[type=\"text\"],\n            #contact input[type=\"email\"],\n            #contact textarea {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div id=\"branding\">\n                <h1><span style=\"color: var(--secondary-color);\"