e about safeguarding your digital assets and ensuring your peace of mind in an increasingly complex threat landscape. We believe in a proactive approach, combining advanced technology with strategic insights to build impenetrable defenses.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get a Free Consultation</h2>\n            <form>\n                <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\">\n                <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\">\n                <textarea placeholder=\"Message\"></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>SecureGuard Cyber Solutions &copy; 2023. All Rights Reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}